  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "In our production we were trying to use `middleware/hosts` to add just a couple of entries from `/etc/hosts` file. At the moment a separate file has to be created even though we only need a couple of lines.\r\n\r\nSince `/etc/hosts` file itself is line based and is rather straightforward, I think it makes sense to support the inline of `/etc/hosts` inside Corefile. That will be especially convenient when only one or two lines of `/etc/hosts` are used.",
